                      OPALEYE MANAGEMENT INC.
                    

•   BOSTON, MA
                          • Investment Advisor
                          • Hedge Fund
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             Opaleye Management is based out of Boston. Opaleye Management is a hedge fund  with  1-10 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $184,938,640 (Form ADV from 2017-03-26).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $200,928,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 56.18%. Opaleye Management's largest holding is Blueprint Medicines Corp with shares held of 880,000.  Opaleye Management has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 16 13Fs and  28 13D/G filings in our database for Opaleye Management. 
                                           






